snippet.title: LEGO® Star Wars™: The Skywalker Saga - Gameplay Overview
snippet.description:
It’s time to take a closer look at gameplay for LEGO® Star Wars™: The Skywalker Saga!
 
Journey to a galaxy far, far away on April 5, 2022!

Pre-Orders are now live! https://go.wbgames.com/LSWG_PreOrder 

The galaxy is yours with LEGO Star Wars™: The Skywalker Saga! Play through all nine saga films in a brand-new video game unlike any other. With over 300 playable characters, over 100 vehicles, and 23 planets to explore, the galaxy has never been more fun!
 
Join us on our Social Channels!
Twitter: https://go.wbgames.com/LSWG-Twitter
Instagram: https://go.wbgames.com/LSWG-Instagram
Facebook: https://go.wbgames.com/LSWG-Facebook
 
#LEGOStarWarsGame #SkywalkerSaga
